    <summary>
      <Value><![CDATA[Pay your council tax, set up a direct debit, check your band, and apply for discounts and exemptions.]]></Value>
    </summary>
    <main>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p class="govuk-body">Council tax helps fund local services including waste collection, planning, parking, and a contribution to the police, fire, and adult social care.</p>]]></Value>
